to a stop or leaves the area.

00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:05.970
The software recognizes that there is movement
and uses the electronic pan, tilt, zoom

00:03:05.970 --> 00:03:09.580
feature of the fisheye camera to follow it
across the field of view and highlight it

00:03:09.580 --> 00:03:11.040
in the top right view frame.

